title: Is two-hour delivery the future of e-commerce? Canadian e-tailer give it a try - 680News
text:
In the U.S., online shopping juggernaut Amazon is experimenting with a service that almost seems too good to be true: one-hour home delivery of purchases. Don't expect to see that delivery option on Amazon.ca anytime soon, but a Vancouver-based e-tailer has come close to matching that offering.
 680News.
